<subSubSection id="C368650B3211980CFF4817B1FC39FF21" lastPageId="28" lastPageNumber="85" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BCD36803211980AFF4817B1FC1CF812" blockId="26.[151,1437,1718,1995]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">
<emphasis id="B906EA923211980AFF4817B1FEF6F916" bold="true" box="[151,330,1718,1743]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">Type material.</emphasis>
According to 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B713211980AFE2417B1FD13F916" author="Suffrian, E." box="[507,687,1718,1743]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref45438" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntniss der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian (1866)</bibRefCitation>
, the type series had been constituted only by females and one specimen should have been housed in 
<collectionCode id="ED63AE453211980AFD9117DCFD06F92B" box="[590,698,1755,1778]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">MNHUB</collectionCode>
. However, a thorough investigation did not produce any positive result, so that the 
<collectingRegion id="49B6F8623211980AFEBF17F9FE1AF8CE" box="[352,422,1790,1815]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">Berlin</collectingRegion>
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFE7217F8FDB8F8CE" box="[429,516,1791,1815]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">syntype</typeStatus>
must be considered lost. On the other hand, two 
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFBEF17F8FB2EF8CE" box="[1072,1170,1791,1815]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">syntypes</typeStatus>
were traced in 
<collectionCode id="ED63AE453211980AFA9E17F8FA25F8CF" box="[1345,1433,1791,1814]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">BMNH</collectionCode>
. The typification has been made as follows. 
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFD561621FCB5F8E0" box="[649,777,1830,1849]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">LECTOTYPE</typeStatus>
: 
<specimenCount id="9D74FD093211980AFCC51624FC93F8E3" box="[794,815,1827,1850]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
, pinned, // “125” [white label, handwritten] // “67.56” [white label, handwritten] // “a D. Suffrian determinat.” [white label, printed] // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D033211980AFBE71641FAB5F886" authority="Guer." authorityName="Guer." box="[1080,1289,1862,1887]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="patagonicus">patagonicus Guer.</taxonomicName>
” [blue label, handwritten] //” 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D033211980AFE97166CFCB8F85A" authority="Suffrian, 1866" authorityName="Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[328,772,1898,1923]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="patagonicus">
<emphasis id="B906EA923211980AFE97166CFDE0F85B" box="[328,604,1899,1923]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">Metallactus patagonicus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B713211980AFDBC166DFCB8F85A" author="Suffrian, E." box="[611,772,1898,1923]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref45438" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntniss der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian, 1866</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFCD51669FC25F858" box="[778,921,1902,1921]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">LECTOTYPUS</typeStatus>
D. Sassi des.” [red label, printed] // (
<collectionCode id="ED63AE453211980AFAE9166CFA2CF85A" box="[1334,1424,1899,1923]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">BMNH</collectionCode>
). The second female, same data, was labelled as 
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFD641689FCEBF87E" box="[699,855,1934,1959]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">paralectotype</typeStatus>
: 
<specimenCount id="9D74FD093211980AFCBC1688FC3AF87E" box="[867,902,1935,1959]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" type="female">1♀</specimenCount>
, pinned, // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D033211980AFBC61689FF73F812" authority="Suffrian, 1866" authorityName="Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="26" pageNumber="83" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="patagonicus">
<emphasis id="B906EA923211980AFBC61689FA8CF87F" box="[1049,1328,1934,1958]" italics="true" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">Metallactus patagonicus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B713211980AFAE51689FF73F812" author="Suffrian, E." pageId="26" pageNumber="83" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref45438" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntniss der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian, 1866</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
<typeStatus id="54C988223211980AFF0916B1FE1DF810" box="[214,417,1974,1993]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">PARALECTOTYPUS</typeStatus>
D. Sassi des.”[red label, printed] // (
<collectionCode id="ED63AE453211980AFCE516B4FC28F812" box="[826,916,1971,1995]" pageId="26" pageNumber="83">BMNH</collectionCode>
).
</paragraph>
